platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Jump in and save the ninjas!

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Goofy banter, diverting puzzles, wall-to-wall actionwe couldnt ask for more from a LEGO Ninjago game. Using the warriors trademark weapons and elemental moves, youll battle the nefarious Ronin and his crew across Chens Island, the Toxic Bogs, and other familiar settings. Even if youve never seen the Masters of Spinjitzu animated series, these hilarious heroes and their kid-friendly shenanigans are guaranteed to win you over.
